                        Mangadex tools
                        ==============

        Overview
        --------

Some useful tools to interface with Mangadex via its JSON API. I foresee two
tools for now:

* mangadex_dl.tcl
    Downloads chapters with varied options

+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Usage: mangadex_dl.tcl [OPTIONS] SERIE_URL [CHAPTER...] |
|                                                         |
| OPTIONS                                                 |
|     -help                                               |
|         Print this help message and exit.               |
|                                                         |
|     -proxy PROXY_URL                                    |
|         Set the curl HTTP/HTTPS proxy.                  |
|                                                         |
|     -first-page PAGE_NO                                 |
|         Start downloading from PAGE_NO (see lrange(n)). |
|                                                         |
|     -last-page PAGE_NO                                  |
|         Stop downloading at PAGE_NO.                    |
|                                                         |
|     -lang LANG_CODE                                     |
|         Only download chapters in this language.        |
|                                                         |
+---------------------------------------------------------+

* mangadex_monitor.tcl (WIP)
    Maintain ATOM feeds for series and automatically download new chapters.


        Dependencies
        ------------

* Tcl 8.6
* tcllib (json module)
* curl
* tdom (mangadex_monitor.tcl only)
